{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/5592","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/5592/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/5592/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/5592/events","html_url":"https://github.com/vuejs/vue/issues/5592","id":226057260,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUyMjYwNTcyNjA=","number":5592,"title":"since v2.3.0, in some specific cases, two consecutive comment vnodes will be merged into one text vnode.","user":{"login":"maggiehe","id":2734387,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI3MzQzODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2734387?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe","html_url":"https://github.com/maggiehe","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/maggiehe/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":5,"created_at":"2017-05-03T17:22:26Z","updated_at":"2017-05-07T13:39:07Z","closed_at":"2017-05-07T13:39:07Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Version\r\n2.3.0\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[https://jsfiddle.net/maggiehe/xovqtqd8/](https://jsfiddle.net/maggiehe/xovqtqd8/)\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nUse the following template with `this.currentIndex = 1`, then check `this._vnode`.\r\n```\r\n<div><div>foo</div><div v-for=\"i in 3\" v-if=\"i===currentIndex\" :key=\"i\">{{i}}</div></div>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nThe template's childNodes will be compiled into: `[\"Element\", \"Element\", \"Comment\", \"Comment\"]`\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nVue(>=2.3.0) compiles the template's childNodes into `[ \"Element\", \"Element\", \"Text\" ]`, while Vue@2.2.6 performs correctly.\r\n\r\n---\r\nThe bug will lead to this error: The client-side rendered virtual DOM tree is not matching server-rendered content.\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->","closed_by":{"login":"yyx990803","id":499550,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ5OTU1MA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/499550?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803","html_url":"https://github.com/yyx990803","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/yyx990803/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/vuejs/vue/issues/5592/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://ap